Package monkey.mnk

Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • monkey.mnk.Position
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class Position
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    A Position refers to a single cell of the Board. It features bounds checking and helper operations.

    1.0
